Package view.GUIView

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Observable<T>
    This interface declares the addObserver method to implement the Observer design pattern
    ReplayObserver
    This class is a Observer (Observer design pattern) used when functionalities of replays are done and must notify observers
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardGUI
    This class is in charge of managing and updating all the CellGUIs when needed.
    BoardRenderer
    This class is a Renderer Swing that designs the ComboBox that shows the various shapes of the board that the user can choose
    CellGUI
    This class represents a cell of the BoardGUI.
    ChooseTeamFromServerDialog
    This class is a JDialog shown if the client has connected to a server that has created a GameTeams game.
    ColorRenderer
    This class is a Renderer Swing that designs the ComboBox that shows the various colors that the user can choose to each of the players
    ControlPanel
    This class is a RolitPanel that shows, depending on the case, the button of save game and the buttons that allow to go forward and backward in the replays.
    DeleteGameDialog
    This class is a Swing JDialog in which the user can delete saved games
    JoinServerDialog
    This class is a Swing JDialog in which the user can join a server
    LoadFileDialog
    This class is a Swing JDialog in which the user can load saved games
    MainWindow
    This class represents the main window in which Rolit is played in GUI Mode
    RankingPanel
    This RolitPanel shows the ranking when the game is finished
    RankingTableModel
    This table model shows a table of each of the rivals' name and score when playing a game
    SaveReplayDialog
    This class is a Swing JDialog in which the user can save the replay of the game
    ServerView
    This class is in charge of showing a GUI that lets the user choose the port in which they want the server to connect
    StatusBar
    This class is a RolitPanel shown at the bottom of the window application that shows the current status of the game or of the replay
    TurnAndRankingBar
    This class is a RolitPanel that gathers the real-time ranking as well as the current turn in the game or replay.
    Tutorial
    This class represents the Rolit tutorial.
    Video
    This class is responsible for reproducing videos.
